spells.description:
Use: Command the Medichopper to attach to your target, absorbing 163,787 damage and granting them 1,266 versatility for 15 sec.

While attached, your healing spells have a chance to refuel the chopper, granting these bonuses to their host again. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Your spells have a chance to imbue the wax, causing it to form into a blazing candle for 15 sec which increases your Versatility by 3,452, further increased by 907 while you remain within its light.
Equip: Don the mantle of the Trashmaster.
